新冠疫情波及海外文娱产业，很多动画和游戏都受到影响。
The new crown epidemic has affected the overseas entertainment industry, many animation and games have been affected.
青春喜相逢。
Rejoice in youth.
大事件。
Major events.
牵一发而动全身。
It's all over me.
。
.
这周，热门动画《恋爱中的小行星》第七话将推迟一周播出。
This week, the popular animation "Asteroid in Love" seventh sentence will be postponed for a week.
原定的播出时间将改为放送总集篇。
The original broadcast time will be changed to a general collection.
。
.
总集篇是一个剪辑已经播出的动画片段，是一个只有在最紧急的时刻才会使用的凑数手段。
An anthology is a clip of an animated segment that has been shown, a ruse that can only be used in the most urgent moments.
很显然，这部动画的制作遇到了很大困难。
Obviously, the production of this animation has encountered great difficulties.
。
.
而这个困难很可能与国内的新冠疫情相关。
That difficulty is likely to be linked to a new crown outbreak at home.
根据推特上面动画师的爆料，由于春节之后疫情没有好转，许多中国的外包公司都处于半歇业的状态，有钱也找不到足够的人手。
According to the cartoonist on Twitter, many Chinese outsourcing companies are semi-closed, unable to find enough money because the epidemic has not improved since the Spring Festival.
外加由于害怕疫情传播，不敢使用纸质素材，只能全数字制作，更加剧了资源的紧缺状况。
In addition, due to fear of the spread of the epidemic, do not dare to use paper materials, can only be fully digital production, exacerbated the scarcity of resources.
。
.
《恋爱中的小行星》是芳文社今年春季主推的拳头作品，在资金和资源的配置上都相对要更宽裕一些。
"Asteroid in Love" is Fang Wenxie this spring's fist works, in capital and resources are relatively more generous allocation.
这样的作品率先停摆，也从一个侧面说明了疫情的影响力。
Such works take the lead in stopping, but also from a side to illustrate the impact of the epidemic.
。
.
国外的游戏行业也不能幸免：顶尖的3A游戏大作有30%-50%的美术素材交由国内代工已经是现在游戏研发的常态。
The gaming industry abroad is not immune: 30% to 50% of the material for top 3A games is now the norm in game development.
。
.
除了中国以外，东南亚的其它国家也是游戏外包的重点地区，而这些国家有些也在疫情的威胁之下。
In addition to China, other countries in Southeast Asia are also the focus of outsourcing, and some of these countries are threatened by the epidemic.
著名外包企业维塔士在新家坡的团队负责《天外世界》Switch版的开发，目前已经因为疫情暂停开发工作，游戏的上市日期也被推迟。
Vitasz's team in Xinjiapo, a leading outsourcing company, is developing the SWITCH version of the game, which has been put on hold because of the epidemic.
从现在的状况来看，这可能只是今年游戏跳票潮的一个开始。
As things stand, this could be just the beginning of this year's jump-ticket boom.
。
.
Private Division宣布因《天外世界》Switch版因疫情跳票。
Private Division announced a ticket jump due to the outbreak of the SWITCH version of Outer Space.
说起Switch，任天堂也是在这场疫情中受到重大打击的游戏企业之一。
Speaking of Switch, Nintendo is one of the game companies that has been hit hard by the epidemic.
由于中美关系的影响，任天堂在去年将美规Switch的生产线迁到了东南亚，但是日规Switch主机和健身环依然都是在中国生产。
Nintendo moved its Standard Switch production line to Southeast Asia last year because of China-US relations, but the Japanese switch and fitness ring are still made in China.
这使得日本市场上Switch供应陷入紧缺，健身环一度断货，而像《动物森友会》限定版主机这样的产品上市日期也无限期推迟。
This has left Japanese markets short of Switch supplies, fitness rings out of business for a while, and products like the limited edition host of Animal Friends have had their launch postponed indefinitely.
。
.
《健身环大冒险》的价格已经涨到了天上，新一代理财产品出炉。
"Fitness Ring Adventure" prices have risen to the sky, a new generation of financial products.
疫情的影响还不只与此。
The epidemic does not stop there.
今年本来是游戏主机换代的大年，按照以往的规律，未来几个月应该是第一批新主机开始逐渐试生产备货的关键阶段。
The next few months should be the critical phase for the first batch of new hosts to begin trial production, according to previous rules.
根据著名投资银行杰富瑞集团本周的一份分析，假如中国工厂停工超过一个月，那么今年年底新上市的两款主机，XBOX X和PS5，都会受到影响。
Two new hosts, XBOX X and PS5, will be hit by the end of the year if Chinese factories shut down for more than a month, according to an analysis by Jeffery Group, a prominent investment bank.
甚至连即将上市的下一代主机，都可能因为新冠疫情而缩减产量，甚至延期。
Even the next generation of hosts that will be on the market could scale back production or even delay production due to the new crowning epidemic.
。
.
当然，也有分析认为，过去一两年里，出于规避风险的考虑，微软和索尼可能都已经做好了将生产线迁往越南、泰国等其它东南亚国家的准备，中国工厂的停工可能不会对新主机上市造成特别严重的影响，主要还是体现在成本上升上。
Of course, some analysts believe Microsoft and Sony may have been prepared to move production to other Southeast Asian countries such as Vietnam and Thailand over the past year or two to avoid risks, and that the shutdown of Chinese plants may not have a particularly serious impact on new mainframe listings, mainly in terms of higher costs.
真正直接遭受冲击的，还是像苹果这样十分依赖富士康等中国代工厂的电子设备企业，一项分析认为苹果可能将有300-500万部手机延迟出货。
The real direct impact is on electronics companies such as Apple, which rely heavily on Chinese subplants such as Foxconn, which one analysis says could delay shipments of 3m to 5m handsets.
。
.
我们不是流行病学的专家，对目前的疫情不好多说什么。
We're not an epidemiologist and we're not saying much about the current epidemic.
或许在现代医学、现代科技的帮助和我们共同的努力下，我们离新冠疫情的拐点已经不远了，也最终会取得胜利——但是这场胜利的代价，也许需要长得多的时间才能够偿还。
Perhaps with the help of modern medicine, modern technology, and our joint efforts, we will not be far from the inflection point of the new crown epidemic, and will ultimately win - but the cost of this victory may be much longer to pay.
。
.
